channel.description:
Ok, before I get started I'd just like to say that I am not hosting this server, but am using it to improve my java "skills". I am just getting familiar with 667's. random.p http://dl.dropbox.com/u/21446948/ggggggg.p
The source does have an Encoder and I was wondering If it had anything to do with that. There are also random file extensions like .e or .s just random extension that I've never seen.
